1.title: This Episode Doesn't Have Its Flying License
1.plot: Meet Reanne Xenos. Reanne toys with nature when she experiments on an alcoholic flirting with rock bottom. The repercussions of her experiment will be a burden the entire Team Allies! family has to bear. Join Barry Sage, Gabe, Ruth, Profit, Alacrity, and a special appearance by Captain Danger as they all go about their ridiculous daily lives in Team Allies!

plot: _Team Allies!_ (qv) is about a team of people with extraordinary superpowers but feel friends and family are a higher priority than world-saving. But don't get too impressed, because world-saving was never high on the priority list.::Ali
